body:
Version 2.1.2

Framework:

- [Imp] BUG-10120 allow to drag sliders slower by using shift key
- [Imp] BUG-10130 Add IParameterFinder support for VST3 plug-ins
        to support "AI knob" control surfaces

- [Fix] BUG-10135 Patch Manager now works with WSL2 EXT4 mounted drives
- [Fix] BUG-10136 Conditional parameter links now work with mouse wheel
- [Fix] BUG-10133 Parameter values now correctly update when dragging controls quickly
- [Fix] Crash when loading plugin on some Linux distributions

OsTIrus:

- [Fix] BUG-10118 Double-clicking in preset name field no longer shows CSS properties

Osirus:

- [Fix] BUG-10106 Hoverland/Galaxpel skins: Rename LFO SHAPE to reverb TYPE
- [Fix] BUG-10106 Galaxpel skin: Reverb Type was not selectable
- [Fix] BUG-10106 Galaxpel skin: Fix swapped
        parameters LFO 3 Keytrack and LFO 3 Fade In
- [Fix] BUG-10106 Hoverland skin: Fix Envelope Polarity button inverted
- [Fix] BUG-10106 If Cutoff Link is active, Cutoff 2 values are displayed
        as offset to Cutoff 1 in range -64 to +63
- [Fix] BUG-10118 Double-clicking in preset name field no longer shows CSS properties
